#11501
Paved road~
Once upon a time there was a busy market here which specialized in food, drink,
and souvenirs for adventurers travelling to and from the city.  Now all that
remains are a few overturned stalls and some smashed up trinkets.  Anything of
any value to anyone has long since been removed.  Not far west of here the city
gates loom omenously, while the road continues to the east into the plains.  
