#11504
Main street~
Once a beautiful street, main street has been reduced to mere rubble, except
for the shell of a shop to the north.  Guards used to be able to climb the city
gates here to defend the city, now the stairs lie at your feet, more twisted
metal.  West of here is a crater which used to be a waterway passing through
the city.  The bridge has been destroyed, but that doesn't matter because no
water will ever pass this way again.    
