#11505
Treasure shop~
Smashed cabinets and some fragments of colored rock remain as a reminder that
this was once a busy treasure shop.  The bones of the proprietor have been
kicked into a corner, one of the last unsavory acts of the people who ransacked
this place.  The only exit is back south to main street.    
