#11506
Midgard creek~
Before the destruction of Midgard, this creek used to flow from the river to
the south to the power station north of here.  It drove a complicated turbine
system which supplied running hot water to the residents of Midgard.  Now, its
just a dried up bed.  North of here is the remains of the turbine, while
south the creek bed joins with the old Midgard river.  Main street continues
east and west.    
