Heart of the turbine.~
Up the creek without a paddle you might say.  The last thing you have time to
wonder before one of the blades of the turbine crashes into the side of your
head is, what possessed you to wander into a still functioning turbine anyway?
Unfortunately, the blade ended it for you before you were able to puzzle out
