End of the river bed~
The river comes to an abrupt halt here as it meets the city wall.  Once upon a
time there was a grate which allowed adventurers to travel out of Midgard into
the outside world.  Now it is so clogged with debris, that there is no hope of
even opening it, let alone actually getting through, which means the only way
to go from here is back west along the river bed.    
