#11515
Market square~
What a mess!  This was obviously the centre of one of the major battles since
everything that could possibly identify it as a market has been destroyed.  
Still, this is market square, which was the hub of activity on the north side
of Midgard before its destruction.  Main street runs east and west from here,
to the north is temple square and the ruins of the great temple of Midgard,
while to the south is the square of commoners.    
