The spam pit~
So this is where all that unwanted mail goes.  Because of the number of
complaints they received from users, the staff of the cyberspace post office
decided to take a more active role in combatting unwanted mail.  The spam pit
is where they dump all the get rich quick schemes, pyramid marketting offers,
and other questionable material that certain cyberspace unsavories insist on
trying to pedal.  This is not a place to linger, you begin to feel
clostrophobic as the spam litterally clammers to be read
